high_descs: Go straight, then turn to your right at the counter to the right of the sink.

Place the tomato in the refrigerator, to the right of the egg, on the second shelf, wait a moment for the tomato to chill, then remove the tomato from the refrigerator.

Place the tomato on the counter, to the right of the paper towels.

drop a tomato in the fridge to cool and then take it out
